node.text:
I did the cover art for the 🔥CULT OF THE LAMB 🔥game by @massivemonsters announced at the #gamescom !!! A weird mixture of animal crossing and a dungeon crawler where you have a cute cult heh 🦑 Both the game and the team behind it are amazing 😭 Going forward i'll work on the game doing some stuff 👀 Also you can see the trailer on youtube! :3 (I attached some screenshots here too!)
.
.
.
